ThoughtsThatYouWouldBeBetterOffDeadOrOfHurtingYourselfInSomeWayInLastTwoWeeksEval is used for a person's stated observation of how often over the last 2 weeks they have been bothered by thoughts they would be better off dead or of hurting themselves in someway, using a four point Likert scale. (National Institute on Drug Abuse (NIDA))
 